00:00:12.881 --> 00:00:14.492
Ningependa kuwashirikisha

00:00:14.492 --> 00:00:17.141
muundo mpya wa helimu ya juu

00:00:17.141 --> 00:00:20.180
muundo ambao ukipanuliwa

00:00:20.180 --> 00:00:22.650
unaweza ukaongeza akili ya pamoja

00:00:22.650 --> 00:00:26.623
ya mamilioni ya watu binafsi
walio na motisha na ubunifu

00:00:26.623 --> 00:00:29.982
ambao vinginevyo wange achwa nyuma.

00:00:29.982 --> 00:00:31.436
tazama ulimwengu

00:00:31.436 --> 00:00:34.258
chagua mahali na upaangazie

00:00:34.258 --> 00:00:38.807
utapata wanadamu wakikimbizana na elimu

00:00:38.807 --> 00:00:40.693
ebu tukutane na wengine wao

00:00:40.693 --> 00:00:42.465
Patrick

00:00:42.465 --> 00:00:44.760
Patrick alizaliwa Liberia

00:00:44.760 --> 00:00:47.770
kwa familia ya watoto ishirini

00:00:47.770 --> 00:00:52.091
Wakati wa vita vya wenyewe kwa wenyewe,
yeye na familia yake walilazimika

00:00:52.091 --> 00:00:54.263
kukimbilia Nigeria.

00:00:54.263 --> 00:00:57.230
huko licha ya hali yake,

00:00:57.230 --> 00:01:01.384
alihitimu sekondari kwa
karibu alama kamili.

00:01:01.384 --> 00:01:04.040
Alitaka kuendelea na elimu ya juu

00:01:04.040 --> 00:01:05.840
lakini kutokana na familia yake

00:01:05.840 --> 00:01:07.672
kuishi katika mstari wa umaskini

00:01:07.672 --> 00:01:09.944
haikuchukua mda, akatumwa Afrika Kusini

00:01:09.944 --> 00:01:12.144
kufanya kazi na kutuma fedha nyumbani

00:01:12.144 --> 00:01:15.000
kulisha familia yake.

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:18.892
Patrick hakuiacha ndoto ya elimu ya juu.

00:01:18.892 --> 00:01:21.244
usiku wa manane, baada ya kazi

00:01:21.244 --> 00:01:25.680
alipekua mtandao akitafuta njia za kusoma.

00:01:25.680 --> 00:01:26.880
Kutana na Debbie.

00:01:26.880 --> 00:01:29.486
Debbie anatoka Florida.

00:01:29.486 --> 00:01:31.704
Wazazi wake hawakuenda chuo,

00:01:31.704 --> 00:01:34.756
wala yeyote wa ndugu zake.

00:01:34.756 --> 00:01:38.036
Debbie amefanya kazi maisha yake yote,

00:01:38.036 --> 00:01:41.847
hulipa kodi, na kujimudu mwezi kwa mwezi,

00:01:41.847 --> 00:01:44.199
akijivunia ndoto ya Marekani,

00:01:44.199 --> 00:01:46.646
ndoto ambayo haiwezi ikawa kamili

00:01:46.646 --> 00:01:48.870
bila elimu ya juu.

00:01:48.870 --> 00:01:51.310
Lakini Debbie hajaweka akiba

00:01:51.310 --> 00:01:52.448
ya elimu ya juu.

00:01:52.448 --> 00:01:54.802
hawezi kulipia masomo,

00:01:54.802 --> 00:01:57.550
wala kuweza kuacha kazi.

00:01:57.550 --> 00:01:59.726
Kutana na Wael.

00:01:59.726 --> 00:02:01.910
Wael ni mkaaji wa Syria.

00:02:01.910 --> 00:02:05.404
anapitia ana kwa ana

00:02:05.404 --> 00:02:07.762
taabu, hofu na kushindwa

00:02:07.762 --> 00:02:10.697
zilizowekewa nchi yake.

00:02:10.697 --> 00:02:13.232
Anaamini sana kwa elimu.

00:02:13.232 --> 00:02:15.672
Alijua kwamba akipata fursa

00:02:15.672 --> 00:02:17.189
ya elimu ya juu,

00:02:17.189 --> 00:02:19.980
fursa ya kutangulia wengine,

00:02:19.980 --> 00:02:22.232
ana nafasi nzuri ya kuishi

00:02:22.232 --> 00:02:26.121
katika dunia iliogeuka kichwa chini.

00:02:26.121 --> 00:02:29.146
Mfumo wa elimu ya juu

00:02:29.146 --> 00:02:32.282
ulifeli Patrick, Debbie na Wael,

00:02:32.282 --> 00:02:34.562
jinsi tu inavyofeli

00:02:34.562 --> 00:02:37.210
mamilioni ya wanafunzi

00:02:37.210 --> 00:02:40.324
mamilioni waliohitimu shule za sekondari

00:02:40.324 --> 00:02:43.690
mamilioni ambao wamefuzu elimu ya juu

00:02:43.690 --> 00:02:45.506
mamilioni wanaotaka kusoma

00:02:45.506 --> 00:02:49.367
bali hawawezi wakapata kwa sababu tofauti.

00:02:49.367 --> 00:02:52.412
Kwanza, za fedha.

00:02:52.412 --> 00:02:55.331
Vyuo vikuu ni ghali. sote twajua

00:02:55.331 --> 00:02:57.459
Maeneo kubwa ulimwenguni

00:02:57.459 --> 00:02:59.827
elimu ya juu haiwezekani

00:02:59.827 --> 00:03:02.283
kwa raia wa kawaida.

00:03:02.283 --> 00:03:04.175
Hii ndio pengine shida kubwa

00:03:04.175 --> 00:03:06.704
inayokumba jamii yetu

00:03:06.704 --> 00:03:10.282
elimu ya juu ilikoma kuwa haki kwa wote

00:03:10.282 --> 00:03:13.971
ikawa teule kwa wachache.

00:03:13.971 --> 00:03:17.940
Pili, tamaduni.

00:03:17.940 --> 00:03:20.882
wanafunzi waliohitimu elimu ya juu,

00:03:20.882 --> 00:03:24.970
wanaojimudu, wanataka masomo, hawawezi

00:03:24.970 --> 00:03:28.266
Kwa sababu haiheshimiki,

00:03:28.266 --> 00:03:30.670
si mahali pa mwanamke.

00:03:30.670 --> 00:03:33.234
Hii ndio taswira ya mamia ya wanawake

00:03:33.234 --> 00:03:35.010
Afrika, Kwa mfano,

00:03:35.010 --> 00:03:37.120
Waliozuiliwa kwa elimu ya juu

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:39.722
kwa sababu ya kinga za tamaduni.

00:03:39.722 --> 00:03:42.110
Na hapa ni sababu ya tatu:

00:03:42.110 --> 00:03:45.742
UNESCO ilisema kuwa mwakani 2025,

00:03:45.742 --> 00:03:48.970
wanafunzi milioni mia moja

00:03:48.970 --> 00:03:51.400
watanyimwa elimu ya juu

00:03:51.400 --> 00:03:55.211
kwa sababu tu, ya kutokua na viti tosha

00:03:55.211 --> 00:03:58.338
kuwapa malazi, kukidhi mahitaji.

00:03:58.338 --> 00:03:59.600
Watafanya mtihani wa usajili,

00:03:59.600 --> 00:04:01.355
wataupita,

00:04:01.355 --> 00:04:03.748
lakini bado hawatapata kuingia

00:04:03.748 --> 00:04:07.416
kwa sababu hakuna nafasi zilizoko

00:04:07.416 --> 00:04:09.320
Hizi ndizo sababu

00:04:09.320 --> 00:04:11.808
Nilianzisha Chuo kikuu cha watu,

00:04:11.808 --> 00:04:14.832
si cha faida, na bila malezi,

00:04:14.832 --> 00:04:16.897
Chuo kinachopeana shahada ya digrii

00:04:16.897 --> 00:04:18.784
kupeana mbadala,

00:04:18.784 --> 00:04:22.376
kujenga mbadala kwa wasio na mwingine

00:04:22.376 --> 00:04:25.952
mbadala ulio nafuu

00:04:25.952 --> 00:04:27.841
na wenye kipimo

00:04:27.841 --> 00:04:30.874
mbadala utakao koroga

00:04:30.874 --> 00:04:33.725
mfumo wa elimu wa sasa

00:04:33.725 --> 00:04:35.613
ufungue milango ya elimu ya juu

00:04:35.613 --> 00:04:37.917
kwa mwanafunzi yeyote aliyehitimu

00:04:37.917 --> 00:04:42.553
bila kujali pato lao, wala wanakoishi,

00:04:42.553 --> 00:04:45.449
ama jamii inavyonena kuwahusu.

00:04:45.449 --> 00:04:47.386
Patrick, Debbie na Wael

00:04:47.386 --> 00:04:48.769
ni mifano tatu tu

00:04:48.769 --> 00:04:51.170
kati ya wanafunzi 1,700 waliokubaliwa

00:04:51.170 --> 00:04:54.889
kutoka nchi 143.

00:04:54.889 --> 00:05:00.150
Sisi - (Makofi) - Asanteni.

00:05:00.150 --> 00:05:02.307
Hatukuitaji kuibuka na gurudumu jipya.

00:05:02.307 --> 00:05:04.605
Tuliangalia tu ni kipi kilikuwa hakifaulu

00:05:04.605 --> 00:05:07.572
na kutumia nguvu ya ajabu ya intaneti

00:05:07.572 --> 00:05:09.466
kukizingira.

00:05:09.466 --> 00:05:12.349
Tuliamua kujenga muundo

00:05:12.349 --> 00:05:15.148
utakao punguza kwa kiwango kikubwa

00:05:15.148 --> 00:05:17.604
gharama ya elimu ya juu

00:05:17.604 --> 00:05:19.743
na hivyo ndivyo tulifanya.

00:05:19.743 --> 00:05:22.639
Kwanza, matofali na chokaa ni gharama.

00:05:22.639 --> 00:05:25.033
Vyuo vikuu vina matumizi

00:05:25.033 --> 00:05:28.423
ambayo vyuo vikuu vya mtandao havina.

00:05:28.423 --> 00:05:30.223
Hatuitaji kupasha gharama hizi

00:05:30.223 --> 00:05:31.939
kwa wanafunzi wetu.

00:05:31.939 --> 00:05:33.309
Hazipo.

00:05:33.309 --> 00:05:36.343
Pia hatufai kubabaishwa na uwezo.

00:05:36.343 --> 00:05:38.552
hakuna mipaka ya viti

00:05:38.552 --> 00:05:40.951
kwa vyuo vikuu vya mtandao.

00:05:40.951 --> 00:05:42.695
Hakika, hakuna anayeitaji kusimama

00:05:42.695 --> 00:05:45.288
nyuma ya ukumbi.

00:05:45.288 --> 00:05:47.327
Vitabu vya kiada pia ni kitu

00:05:47.327 --> 00:05:49.844
wanafunzi wetu hawaitaji kununua.

00:05:49.844 --> 00:05:52.731
Kwa kutumia raisilimali za elimu ya wazi

00:05:52.731 --> 00:05:55.211
na ukarimu wa maprofesa

00:05:55.211 --> 00:05:56.980
wanaoweka nyenzo zao

00:05:56.980 --> 00:05:59.659
bure na zinapatikana,

00:05:59.659 --> 00:06:02.539
Hatuitaji kutuma wanafunzi
wetu kununua vitabu vya kiada,

00:06:02.539 --> 00:06:05.635
nyenzo zetu zote zinakuja bure

00:06:05.635 --> 00:06:07.283
hata maprofesa,

00:06:08.283 --> 00:06:11.160
Ule mustari ghali kabisa
kwa mizania ya chuo kikuu chochote,

00:06:11.160 --> 00:06:12.610
huja bure kwa wanafunzi wetu,

00:06:12.610 --> 00:06:15.163
zaidi ya 3,000 yao

00:06:15.163 --> 00:06:18.753
wakiwemo Marais, makamu wa machancellor,

00:06:18.753 --> 00:06:21.648
maprofesa na washauri wa kitaaluma

00:06:21.648 --> 00:06:25.144
kutoka vyuo vikuu kama vile NYU,

00:06:25.144 --> 00:06:27.224
Yale, Berkely, na Oxford,

00:06:27.224 --> 00:06:30.153
wakajiunga nasi kuwasaidia wanafunzi wetu.

00:06:30.153 --> 00:06:34.422
Hatimaye, ni imani yetu kwa masomo ya rika kwa rika.

00:06:34.422 --> 00:06:37.543
Tunatumia huu muundo wa ufundishaji imara

00:06:37.543 --> 00:06:40.271
kuwapa moyo wanafunzi kutoka kote duniani

00:06:40.271 --> 00:06:42.598
kuingiliana na kujifunza pamoja

00:06:42.598 --> 00:06:45.823
na pia kupunguza mda

00:06:45.823 --> 00:06:50.327
Maprofesa wetu wanaohitaji kujizatiti kwa
kazi ya mazoezi darasani.

00:06:52.879 --> 00:06:58.086
Kama intaneti imetufanya 
kijiji cha kimataifa,

00:06:58.086 --> 00:07:02.454
muundo huu unaweza kuuendeleza
uongozi wake wa usoni.

00:07:02.454 --> 00:07:04.310
Angalia vile tunavyoifanya.

00:07:04.310 --> 00:07:07.150
Tunatoa mipango miwili tu:

00:07:07.150 --> 00:07:09.638
utawala kibiashara na sayansi ya kompyuta,

00:07:09.638 --> 00:07:11.287
hiyo mipango miwili

00:07:11.287 --> 00:07:13.848
ndio inayosakwa sana duniani kote,

00:07:13.848 --> 00:07:15.653
hiyo mipango miwili ndio yenye uwezo mkubwa

00:07:15.653 --> 00:07:19.222
kuwasaidia wanafunzi wetu kupata ajira.

00:07:19.222 --> 00:07:22.274
Wanafunzi wetu wanapokubalika,

00:07:22.274 --> 00:07:25.779
huwekwa kwa darasa dogo

00:07:25.779 --> 00:07:29.265
la wanafunzi 20 kwenda 30 kuhakikisha

00:07:29.265 --> 00:07:32.738
wanaohitaji usaidizi binafsi wanapata.

00:07:32.738 --> 00:07:36.510
Zaidi ya hayo, kwa kila kozi ya wiki tisa,

00:07:36.510 --> 00:07:38.614
hukutana na rika mpya,

00:07:38.614 --> 00:07:40.508
kundi nzima la wanafunzi wapya

00:07:40.508 --> 00:07:42.254
kutoka kote ulimwenguni.

00:07:42.254 --> 00:07:45.302
Kila wiki, wanapoingia darasani,

00:07:45.302 --> 00:07:48.222
wanapata maelezo ya hotuba ya wiki,

00:07:48.222 --> 00:07:50.254
zoezi la kusoma, zoezi la ziada,

00:07:50.254 --> 00:07:51.770
na swali la majadiliano,

00:07:51.770 --> 00:07:54.478
ambayo ni msingi wa masomo yetu,

00:07:54.478 --> 00:07:55.780
Kila wiki, kila mwanafunzi

00:07:55.780 --> 00:07:58.887
lazima achangie kwa mjadala darasani

00:07:58.887 --> 00:08:00.760
na pia lazima atoe maoni

00:08:00.760 --> 00:08:03.174
kwa michango ya wengine.

00:08:03.174 --> 00:08:06.517
Kwa njia hii, tunafungua akili za wanafunzi wetu,

00:08:06.517 --> 00:08:09.365
tunakuza mwelekeo chanya

00:08:09.365 --> 00:08:12.165
kuelekea tamaduni tofauti.

00:08:12.165 --> 00:08:14.101
Mwisho wa kila wiki,

00:08:14.101 --> 00:08:15.747
wanafunzi hufanya jaribio,

00:08:15.747 --> 00:08:17.201
wanawasilisha kazi za ziada,

00:08:17.201 --> 00:08:18.940
ambazo hukaguliwa na wenzao

00:08:18.940 --> 00:08:22.285
kwa usimamizi wa waalimu,

00:08:22.285 --> 00:08:24.661
pata alama, enda kwa wiki nyingine.

00:08:24.661 --> 00:08:27.112
Mwisho wa kozi, hufanya mtihani wa mwisho,

00:08:27.112 --> 00:08:32.703
pata alama, na kuenda kwa kozi nyingine.

00:08:32.703 --> 00:08:35.152
Tulifungua milango ya elimu ya juu

00:08:35.152 --> 00:08:38.871
kwa mwanafunzi yeyote aliyehitimu.

00:08:38.871 --> 00:08:41.799
Mwanafunzi yeyote aliyehitimu sekondari,

00:08:41.799 --> 00:08:44.957
kingereza tosha na muunganisho wa intaneti

00:08:44.957 --> 00:08:46.402
anaweza kusoma na sisi.

00:08:46.402 --> 00:08:49.168
Hatutumii redio. Hatutumii video.

00:08:49.168 --> 00:08:51.816
upana wa bendi si hoja.

00:08:51.816 --> 00:08:54.210
Mwanafunzi yeyote kutoka kokote duniani

00:08:54.210 --> 00:08:56.222
aliye na mwuunganisho wowote wa intaneti

00:08:56.222 --> 00:08:58.606
anaweza kusoma nasi.

00:08:58.606 --> 00:09:00.797
tuko malezi-huru.

00:09:00.797 --> 00:09:03.140
tuulizacho tu wanafunzi wetu kukidhi

00:09:03.140 --> 00:09:04.884
ni gharama ya mitihani yao,

00:09:04.884 --> 00:09:07.396
Dola 100 kwa kila mtihani.

00:09:07.396 --> 00:09:10.070
Mwanafunzi wa muda kamili 
wa digrii ya hahada ya kwanza

00:09:10.070 --> 00:09:12.020
anayechukua kozi 40,

00:09:12.020 --> 00:09:14.868
atalipa dola 1,000 kwa mwaka,

00:09:14.868 --> 00:09:17.564
Dola 4,000 kukamilisha digrii,

00:09:17.564 --> 00:09:21.030
na kwa wale hawawezi kumudu hata hii,

00:09:21.030 --> 00:09:23.667
tunawapa udhamini aina mbali mbali.

00:09:23.667 --> 00:09:26.972
Ni dhamira yetu kuwa hakuna
atakayeachwa nyuma

00:09:26.972 --> 00:09:29.100
kwa sababu za kifedha.

00:09:29.100 --> 00:09:32.563
Kwa wanafunzi 5,000 mwaka wa 2016,

00:09:32.563 --> 00:09:37.260
muundo huu ni endelevu kifedha.

00:09:37.260 --> 00:09:41.857
Miaka mitano iliyopita, yalikuwa maono.

00:09:41.857 --> 00:09:44.714
Leo, ni halisi.

00:09:44.714 --> 00:09:47.075
Mwezi jana, hatimaye tulipata

00:09:47.075 --> 00:09:50.325
muhuri wa kitaaluma kwa muundo wetu.

00:09:50.325 --> 00:09:54.259
Chuo kikuu cha watu sasa kina kibali rasmi

00:09:54.259 --> 00:09:55.407
(Makofi)

00:09:55.407 --> 00:10:01.307
Asanteni.

00:10:01.307 --> 00:10:02.951
Kwa kibali hichi,

00:10:02.951 --> 00:10:06.052
ni wakati wetu sasa kupaa

00:10:06.052 --> 00:10:09.953
Tumeonyesha kwamba muundo wetu
unafanya kazi.

00:10:09.953 --> 00:10:13.280
nakaribisha vyuo vikuu, na maana zaidi,

00:10:13.280 --> 00:10:14.985
serikali za nchi zinazokua,

00:10:14.985 --> 00:10:16.650
kuiga muundo huu

00:10:16.650 --> 00:10:19.790
kuhakikisha milango ya elimu ya juu

00:10:19.790 --> 00:10:22.160
itapanuka zaidi.

00:10:22.160 --> 00:10:24.450
Enzi mpya inakuja

00:10:24.450 --> 00:10:26.978
enzi itakayo shuhudia

00:10:26.978 --> 00:10:29.678
kuvurugika kwa elimu ya juu

00:10:29.678 --> 00:10:31.428
kama tunvyoijua leo,

00:10:31.428 --> 00:10:35.864
kutoka kuwa teule kwa wachache

00:10:35.864 --> 00:10:38.238
kuenda kuwa haki ya kimsingi,

00:10:38.238 --> 00:10:41.535
